$ VBA Module Text [Common]

The function `regexpSplit` splits a given input string on a → development/languages/JavaScript/objects/String/regular-expression[regular expression].
(See also → development/languages/VBA/regular-expressions[regular expressions in VBA]).

`rpad` and `lpad` pads a string on the left or right side with spaces, or optionally any other character.

